&lt;p&gt;Woodchurch ward is a ward caring for predominantly older adults with a varied mental health conditions. We are part of Thanet Mental Health In-Patient services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;he role involves providing care and support to our patients currently experiencing mental health difficulties requiring an inpatient admission for assessment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Commitment to meeting the needs of people with mental health problems and valuing their rights is a pre-requisite.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The inpatient service is now recruiting band 5 Staff Nurses for a key roles in an expanding team of nurses and support workers. You will be motivated, flexible, interested and ready to work in a challenging but very rewarding environment, where the client is at the centre of all our interventions. If your application is successful, you will be notified by e-mail. Therefore, please ensure that you regularly check your NHS jobs account.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
